Ratings for NFL playoff games are down close to double digits so
far this season, a surprising reality that has spawned all manner of busine=
ss philosophizing=E2=80=94some of it banal, some of it quite sage.

John Ourand ( https://puck.news/author/john-ourand/?utm_campaign=3DThe+Vars=
ity+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%281%2F23%2F25%29&utm_content=3DThe+Varsity+-+SUBSCRIBERS=
